17:33.302 --> 17:34.888
Wow.

17:34.929 --> 17:37.432
If you dig deep, like,
down in the sediment

17:37.433 --> 17:38.683
down there, the riverbed?

17:38.725 --> 17:41.101
Man, it's spicy.

17:41.143 --> 17:43.103
You feel enlightened yet?

17:43.145 --> 17:46.148
Look how the color's
changed in the broth.

17:46.190 --> 17:49.360
♪

