Is it what you kind of expected?

17:55.950 --> 17:57.117
Hotpot?

17:57.159 --> 17:59.370
Yes, it is exactly
what I expected it.

18:01.748 --> 18:03.124
- More beers, guys?

18:03.125 --> 18:04.500
- Yeah, definitely.

