21:36.963 --> 21:41.175
The Chinese invented being
obsessed with food.

21:43.052 --> 21:44.929
They invented, you
know, being obsessed

21:44.971 --> 21:47.932
with the providence of
ingredients with going

21:47.933 --> 21:50.350
to a particular place
- for a particular dish.

21:48.849 --> 21:50.350
- Right.

21:50.392 --> 21:53.353
So they've had that tradition
for at least 800 years.

21:53.395 --> 21:55.397
Fuchsia Dunlop has
had an extraordinary

21:55.439 --> 21:58.358
relationship with China,
and Sichuan in particular,

21:58.400 --> 22:02.029
since she first arrived
here as a student in 1994.

22:02.071 --> 22:05.554
She was the first foreigner
to study at the Sichuan

22:05.555 --> 22:07.034
Higher Institute of Cuisine

22:07.076 --> 22:09.162
and has written numerous
books about her experiences

22:09.203 --> 22:10.913
and about Sichuanese food,

22:10.914 --> 22:12.623
which are rightly considered

22:12.665 --> 22:14.374
groundbreaking and definitive.

22:14.416 --> 22:16.543
To say she was way
ahead of her time,

22:16.585 --> 22:19.379
is an understatement.

22:19.421 --> 22:22.549
She's brought us to chef
Lan Gui Jin's restaurant,

22:22.591 --> 22:24.406
-Yu Zhi Lan.

22:24.407 --> 22:28.326
- What he's trying to do
is sort of raise the level

22:28.327 --> 22:32.392
of Sichuanese food
to sort of, um,

22:32.434 --> 22:35.353
very refined banquet cookery.

22:38.024 --> 22:41.401
Is what he's doing unusual
for Chengdu, for China?

22:41.443 --> 22:43.297
It's really unusual because
I think in the West,

22:43.321 --> 22:46.032
we're so very used to the
idea of a celebrity chef

22:46.073 --> 22:48.575
and the individual
chef as artist.

22:48.617 --> 22:50.036
But in China, people
traditionally

22:50.077 --> 22:51.411
look down on chefs.

22:51.453 --> 22:52.872
So this is quite a new thing.

22:52.913 --> 22:54.874
There are very few
chefs who really like

22:54.915 --> 22:58.002
the creative vision
behind the food

22:58.044 --> 23:00.420
and doing the work
in the kitchen.

23:00.462 --> 23:02.215
♪

