Delicate flavors like lily buds

23:07.887 --> 23:10.451
scented with rose petals
are presented alongside

23:10.452 --> 23:13.037
more assertive tastes like
thinly sliced, brazed

23:13.038 --> 23:14.601
beef shank with chili oil.

23:14.643 --> 23:17.813
Tea tree mushrooms blanched
and lightly stir fried

23:17.855 --> 23:19.232
with Chinese stem lettuce.

23:19.273 --> 23:22.568
And you suggest starting with the...
Lily buds?

23:22.569 --> 23:25.612
Yeah, I would start with the
lily buds 'cause they're

23:23.694 --> 23:25.612
nice and oiled, yeah.

23:25.654 --> 23:28.074
♪

23:28.115 --> 23:29.471
-It's nice texture.

23:29.472 --> 23:30.826
- Yeah.

23:30.868 --> 23:32.828
That's... those mushrooms
are amazing.

23:32.870 --> 23:34.621
Yeah, I love these cashew nuts.

23:34.663 --> 23:37.833
Also prawns served cold
with handmade noodles

23:37.875 --> 23:41.045
dressed with natural
vegetable extracts.

23:41.087 --> 23:43.672
So you've probably been
having all kinds of amazing

23:43.673 --> 23:45.508
Sichuanese flavors
because Sichuan,

23:45.509 --> 23:48.261
it's not just about chili
and Sichuan pepper,

23:46.175 --> 23:48.261
it's about fujawei.

23:48.302 --> 23:51.264
Complex, layered flavors
like French sauces.

23:51.305 --> 23:53.473
- Yes.
- And there's one of them called guai wei,

23:53.515 --> 23:54.850
Strange flavor.

23:54.892 --> 23:56.352
-  "Strange flavor."
- Yeah.

23:56.394 --> 23:58.854
Because it's a mixture
of sweet, sour, salty,

23:58.896 --> 24:01.274
spicy, numbing, and
nutty all together.

24:01.315 --> 24:04.277
And this is strange
flavor noodles.

24:04.318 --> 24:06.486
So it's just like a real
traditional Sichuan dish

24:06.528 --> 24:08.364
but done in a very refined way.

24:08.406 --> 24:09.657
Then some soup.

