A rich, slow simmered
chicken and pork stock,

24:12.534 --> 24:14.661
a raft of chopped
meat floats on top

24:14.703 --> 24:16.705
to clarify the broth.

24:16.747 --> 24:18.374
A small bundle of
impossibly thin

24:18.416 --> 24:21.335
hand-cut noodles made
with duck egg yolks,

24:21.377 --> 24:23.670
a Western Sichuan specialty.

24:23.712 --> 24:26.506
[chef speaks
Sichuanese Mandarin]

24:26.548 --> 24:28.529
- Okay.

24:28.530 --> 24:30.510
- [chef speaks
Sichuanese Mandarin]

