Okay, so he's saying, um,
first, um, have a smell

24:33.931 --> 24:38.311
of this and then, um, and
then taste the broth.

24:38.352 --> 24:41.439
♪

24:42.731 --> 24:44.691
Oh, it's beautiful.

24:44.733 --> 24:46.944
And just... just gently
press the noodles.

24:46.986 --> 24:48.362
[chef speaks
Sichuanese Mandarin]

